node.text:
With the New York Academy derby approaching, every player is hoping for a chance to impress when it matters.
 
“We’re two New York City based teams and we just want to let them know that we’re the better team.”
 
[From B/R Football x @audi] #GoalsDriveProgress

node.text:
“Off the field you’re missing your family, missing your home, it can affect you on the field.” Through the homestay program, The Academy makes sure players from all over the country feel at home.

[From B/R Football x @audi] #GoalsDriveProgress

node.title: A home away from home at The Academy
